Enhance your Smart Home experience with WOOMO's products.

If you own an Alexa Echo Show, you can ask Alexa Echo Show to display the live view from your WOOMO.

Follow the steps here to connect your WOOMO account to Alexa:
1. Download the "WOOMO" app from the app store;
2. Register a WOOMO account to add your devices;
3. Configure your devices and name the devices;
4. Download the "Alexa" app from the app store;
5. Configure Alexa Echo Show in the "Alexa" app;
6. Search for "WOOMO" from the skills category in the "Alexa" app;
7. Enable "WOOMO" skill, and you'll be navigated to WOOMO's login page;
8. Log into your WOOMO account to finish.


Once the "WOOMO" Skill is enabled, simply ask Alexa to control your WOOMO devices by their names. For example:
“Alexa, show (name of device)"
“Alexa, stop"

If you experience any problems while using this skill, please contact us at support@woomotech.com
